    "content": "Out Of Touch\r\nAlthough this single by Daryl Hall & John Oats topped the US Billboard\r\nCharts in late 1984, it only reached number 48 in the UK.\r\nTab by bass50611. Not exact as original but close. Note all the pause dots\r\nAnd syncopation in verse and pre-chorus. Comments is bass254@btinternet.com \r\n\r\n[tab]Intro:        [     Play This x4         ]\r\n                  .          .          .\r\nG|------------|---------------------------\r\nD|-DRUM START-|--------------5------------\r\nA|---4 BARS---|------------5--------------\r\nE|------------|-0-1-------------5---3---5-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]     .          .      .\r\nG|-----------------------\r\nD|--------------5--------\r\nA|------------5----------\r\nE|-0-1-----------------5-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse:\r\n   .        .           .         .      .        .          .\r\nG|------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nD|-5------3-5---------------------3----3-5------3-5------------------3----\r\nA|-------5------------555-----5-5--------------5-----------555----5-5-----\r\nE|----------------011----------------------------------011-------------33-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Pre-Chorus:                 .                             .\r\nG|----------------------------------------------------------\r\nD|-------------7--7-5---333-2-------------------------------\r\nA|-3-33---3-5-7-----------------5-5--------3-33---1---0---5-\r\nE|-----------------------------------3-33-------------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus 1:\r\n   .       .           .     .        .          .     .       .   (Break)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nD|---------5--------------------------5------------------------5-------\r\nA|--------5--------------------------5------------------------5--------\r\nE|-1-----------5---3---5---0-1-----------5---3---5---0-1-------------5-[/tab]\r\n\r\nRepeat Verse & Pre-Chorus:\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus 2:\r\n   .       .           .   